WEBVTT

00:00:00:000 --> 00:00:01:000
PayPal

00:00:02:000 --> 00:00:04:000
Did you know

00:00:06:000 --> 00:00:09:000
you don't have to add money

00:00:09:000 --> 00:00:11:000
to your PayPal balance

00:00:11:000 --> 00:00:14:000
to use PayPal for things like

00:00:15:000 --> 00:00:19:000
shopping

00:00:20:000 --> 00:00:21:000
and

00:00:21:000 --> 00:00:25:000
sending money

00:00:25:000 --> 00:00:28:000
When you don't have money in your PayPal balance,

00:00:28:000 --> 00:00:31:000
the purchases and the money you send

00:00:31:000 --> 00:00:34:000
come directly from your linked bank account

00:00:34:000 --> 00:00:37:000
or your linked debit or credit card.

00:00:37:000 --> 00:00:39:000
Don't have a linked payment method?

00:00:39:000 --> 00:00:42:000
In your Wallet,

00:00:43:000 --> 00:00:45:000
click Link a Payment Method.

00:00:45:000 --> 00:00:48:000
Pick the method you want to use,

00:00:48:000 --> 00:00:51:000
then give us your account details.

00:00:52:000 --> 00:00:54:000
We'll use that source

00:00:54:000 --> 00:00:56:000
whenever you send money

00:00:56:000 --> 00:00:58:000
or make a purchase.

00:00:59:000 --> 00:01:01:000
Fast. Simple. Secure.

00:01:02:000 --> 00:01:03:000
PayPal
